---
title: Spiced Chickpea Wraps with Cucumber Raita and Spinach Salad
description: Chana masala is a dish eaten all over India, and while each regional version has its very own personality, it's always fragrant and 100% delicious! In our rendition, we've taken these classic flavours and put them in a delicious warm wrap, served with homemade cucumber raita and a spinach salad with plenty of crunch!
